---
title: Pumpkin & Veggie Israeli Couscous Salad with Honey Dressing, Herby Mayo & Crumbly Cheese
description: This delightful dish is a celebration of wholesome roasted veggies with Israeli couscous and fragrant herbs. Add crumbly cheese
and roasted almonds for extra flavour and crunch, then top it off with a drizzle of dill-parsley dressing.

